  "text": "I am assuming that she sits between the different colored columns. One on her left and one on her right. The dark one is on her left. To indicate at this position an equal opportunity, you might say, for potentiation of the mind to be of the negative or positive paths. Ra comment on this. I am Ra. Although this is correct, it is not as perceptive as the notice that the a priestess, as this figure has been called, sits within a structure in which polarity is symbolized, as you correctly noted, by the light and a dark appealers is an integral and necessary part. The unfed mind has no polarity, just as intelligent infinity has none. The nature of the sub sub logos, which offers the third identity experience is one of polarity, not by choice, but by careful design.",
